title: My Top 500 Greatest Songs
description:
These are my favourite 500 songs... so far, 'cause it changes continually.


I made this, because I thought that the 'Rolling Stone' magazines top 500 ignores a lot of 'newer' songs... although I'm also a big fan of the 50s & 60s sound.


This best of includes a huge range of different genres and also a few german songs
... cause I'm Austrian ;)


I hope you enjoy this torrent and pls seed!


And pls tell me how you like it! ;)
